column5: Ouch! I know about muskies, I had eight stitches in my left thumbthanks to one.
will not be fishing with flip flops any more Thats not an attack. as forest gump would say,stupid is as stupid does. he needs to learn how to handel toothy criters
Just wondering....what is the musky limit for humans? At least this musky observed catch and release!!
Would a sweaty foot qualify as stink bait?
I was always worried about that when I was a kid but when I became an adult I convinced myself that could never happen...
